lead_paragraph: South Africa opener Quinton de Kock hit a masterful 178 runs in a comfortable six-wicket victory over top-ranked Australia on Friday in the first one-day international of the five-match series.

headline.print_headline: De Kock Blasts South Africa to ODI Win Against Australia
